    TypeAliasManagerPE

    public class TypeAliasManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manager for saxon:type-alias declarations in a stylesheet. Saxon extension introduced in Saxon 9.8 This is a dummy version for Saxon-HE: the feature requires Saxon-PE or higher
